{"tid":579694,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［外地撚］深夜食堂 - 雞胸配薯仔沙律菜","createTime":"2018-03-03T21:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T03:24:26.000Z","uid":54581,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ecb550a080c7fe3f474e2899e78efc3219a867","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T21:10:07.000Z","msg":"開定先 過一個鐘後左右開始煮<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n<br />\n雞胸一塊<br />\n<br />\n薯仔一大個<br />\n<br />\n沙律菜半包<br />\n<br />\n大陸雙熊貓牌生抽王一枝<br />\n<br />\n鹽&amp;胡椒粉少許<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工具：<br />\n<br />\n不繡鋼煲一個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廢事洗多個煎pan<br />\n打算一個煲搞撚掂晒所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖後補"},{"pid":"b00bb4570279cad7eef73a923584536926e3e829","tid":579694,"uid":4550,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T22:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/062822_907568abfcb8e15a2a931d82a14c3943.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F062822_907568abfcb8e15a2a931d82a14c3943.gif&h=8a26fc7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/062823_907568abfcb8e15a2a931d82a14c3943.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F062823_907568abfcb8e15a2a931d82a14c3943.gif&h=62316cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPo定先"},{"pid":"e1599d807c400c7f3d547b1f68d41cdec2ba9065","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:01:36.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母 枝大陸生抽蓋都開唔撚到<br />\n<br />\n宣布下次再續<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/070024_bdecb25f87277fb7add55e76bf87e24e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F070024_bdecb25f87277fb7add55e76bf87e24e.png&h=b4ce9827&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c14f1bb64842fdf38b548d9bd4943b9d9406572","tid":579694,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b0730380fe9911b4583c07aa0f270c569f7783","tid":579694,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a4793557a186bb77139e49a28f045ec9f57c3f","tid":579694,"uid":77134,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:10:28.000Z","msg":"整沙律落生抽 你老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041d3ceee0891b27b914cf1a866741062fdb39cb","tid":579694,"uid":113546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:12:38.000Z","msg":"咁小事就放棄<br />\n搵把刀𠝹開佢繼續"},{"pid":"a608f3b1054f4f308c5c5307a15af3d53f4ddf61","tid":579694,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:13:52.000Z","msg":"今次都開唔到下次就會開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續啦仆街"},{"pid":"6f0836929071c453bce95e64b7f8e4752574bd68","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:14:19.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你以為我會為左枝傻鳩同自己晚餐鬥氣?<br />\n<br />\n幾經波折終於搵刀撬開佢個閪口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搵兩茶匙生抽 少少鹽 胡椒粉（黑） 同辣粉搞佢廿分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/071418_bc88a43d0e8ee44755cbc320f1debc80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F071418_bc88a43d0e8ee44755cbc320f1debc80.png&h=23752e42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a7b59c7b64c9c28703fb6c47b95d148493900d9","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:36:27.000Z","msg":"跟住係預備薯仔<br />\n<br />\n洗緊既時候on99起泡唔知做咩<br />\n嚇到我搵洗髮精摔左兩野個薯仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住要切件 最好細粒啲 易整好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n切到靚靚仔仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/073255_b75499ad4f21010ec20a74e10b9832dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F073255_b75499ad4f21010ec20a74e10b9832dd.png&h=80cd9118&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/073257_ea672ca14bdd504389ba6de55e13ce54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F073257_ea672ca14bdd504389ba6de55e13ce54.png&h=f56a9b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n燒熱個pan <br />\n<br />\n油滾後再落薯仔慢火煎香佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/073259_1212cac9a5f11fb3504760c2cf2f56ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F073259_1212cac9a5f11fb3504760c2cf2f56ab.png&h=f9263b48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/073301_f78eaff05d1de51d1303a5faa7473e73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F073301_f78eaff05d1de51d1303a5faa7473e73.png&h=a15dd1f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c828ca666a5aa11c45f866180fffbfd405a72ac2","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:47:48.000Z","msg":"煎到佢開始黑黑地就落雞胸 大火爆香佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/074540_397e186097d718f5e120c94ed14db1d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F074540_397e186097d718f5e120c94ed14db1d7.png&h=b87400cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下幾撚靚 有仙氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/074547_f1707b0ea2896d08b1685298f2586cbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F074547_f1707b0ea2896d08b1685298f2586cbe.png&h=5eee833f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc304784a713f6608adc718ed9ba972e6b0dc529","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:49:27.000Z","msg":"跟住我就加水（300ml)<br />\n又係鹽同胡椒粉<br />\n<br />\n跟手整多三茶匙生抽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/074805_b7435bd105541e452e793f1de8def82e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F074805_b7435bd105541e452e793f1de8def82e.png&h=29e27898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大火滾到佢起泡就轉中火憫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/074806_b4d2f1e9eda0331fb353dee57c6af27e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F074806_b4d2f1e9eda0331fb353dee57c6af27e.png&h=84c662f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc67392e8c97e5877c112dcb376106bcacecfebe","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T23:52:59.000Z","msg":"最後一個拼圖就係個沙律菜<br />\n<br />\n洗好佢先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/075257_666a022c04f63472864eb6d906c08217.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F075257_666a022c04f63472864eb6d906c08217.png&h=c7c0ebbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7718a8858328fd8b12f5b229386f513a05bb1264","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:02:50.000Z","msg":"由於唔知點解煮極都唔收水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我落埋菜落去煲多幾分鐘就收爐了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/080248_9c367f4055b94f687200f5c08b83b07e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F080248_9c367f4055b94f687200f5c08b83b07e.png&h=a0d5d37c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37cf47ceae6f8e21a28247d4fc9ef466abd04e44","tid":579694,"uid":139509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:05:36.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你老味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dca4024f2c7e36400e5610f84832f85e6321e16","tid":579694,"uid":49176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:08:20.000Z","msg":"仆街...真係食開屎?"},{"pid":"1ae7b643dd7117fbc62fa565cb6c7487f0f8aeae","tid":579694,"uid":15186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:10:29.000Z","msg":"baby spanish 咁煮真係好噁心"},{"pid":"9d21a831d7d8e7d703eeee34aa825eca2a4c35a6","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:14:34.000Z","msg":"完成品：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n薯仔： 幾淋下 咬落外脆內沙，一流<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雞胸： 好撚juicy, 吸晒腌料啲味，有口感，超一流<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沙律菜： 煮煮下唔撚見晒，懷疑溶咁啲，僅存既好有菜既鮮味 同個汁相映成趣，一流！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n估唔到第一次煮大餐就咁成功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/081433_38f82185a2e299a77a2c6583ccb65ceb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F081433_38f82185a2e299a77a2c6583ccb65ceb.png&h=fb145465&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebe7760f80baaa5ff256f2caa1498359498b9922","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:17:26.000Z","msg":"下次應該開個post 叫是日早餐 餓撚勿入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4589fb9c3885ed8042240fd57255389fe7ca54","tid":579694,"uid":115171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:23:33.000Z","msg":"睇黎樓豬真係食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6baf0c199c0264f03ded71cc6b3d6af5d03c3b8c","tid":579694,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:24:43.000Z","msg":"煮個沙律都整成3個鐘"},{"pid":"de718ccd396427827768683dc28b5379efcef88c","tid":579694,"uid":31733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:27:12.000Z","msg":".........<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢堆野....真係食得落咩"},{"pid":"3003b18937298b8959f489adac95ef915ae7f565","tid":579694,"uid":172093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:42:06.000Z","msg":"一係直接加d咖哩粉做咖哩算啦<br />\n一係就切粒再烚熟d薯仔加埋d沙律菜撈沙律醬食<br />\n雞胸就煎左下佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370a8b7cbb22d7ba8b57e46dae01004d30f54c06","tid":579694,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3003b18937298b8959f489adac95ef915ae7f565","tid":579694,"uid":172093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:42:06.000Z","msg":"一係直接加d咖哩粉做咖哩算啦<br />\n一係就切粒再烚熟d薯仔加埋d沙律菜撈沙律醬食<br />\n雞胸就煎左下佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T00:50:03.000Z","msg":"模仿緊網上薯仔憫雞食譜"},{"pid":"1629a8a9a2c0cd8803c22cf44150c8cb1a0894cd","tid"